{{Youmay|the Security Council of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]]|the [[New Republic]] [[security council]]}}
{{Quote|No one sent me. I am Captain Typho of Naboo, formerly of the Senate Security Council. I am here on my own. No agency or individual has sanctioned my undertaking.|Typho, to [[Aurra Sing/Legends|Aurra Sing]]|<ref name="sos">''[[Coruscant Nights II: Street of Shadows]]''</ref>}}
The '''Senate Security Council''' or '''Security Council''' was a group amongst the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] that was charged with overseeing the security of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

Among the Security Council's list of powers was the authority to initiate [[Order 65/Legends|Order 65]], a contingency command instructing all units of the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] that the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] had been declared a threat to the Galactic Republic and was to be apprehended or terminated if necessary. Unlike its counterpart, [[Order 66/Legends|Order 66]], Order 65 was never enacted.

